Class IntField

  • java.lang.Object
    • db.Field
      • db.IntField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Field>
    public class IntField
extends Field
    IntField provides a wrapper for 4-byte signed integer data which is read or written to a Record.
